tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE building_blueprints (
    blueprint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_name VARCHAR(50),
    architect_name VARCHAR(50),
    building_type VARCHAR(50),
    blueprint_content JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE Blueprints (
    blueprint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    blueprint_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    architect_id INT,
    blueprint_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (architect_id) REFERENCES Architects(architect_id)
);

CREATE TABLE buildings (
    building_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    building_name VARCHAR,
    architect_id INT,
    location VARCHAR,
    year_built INT
);

CREATE TABLE Architects (
  architect_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name STRING,
  email STRING,
  specialty STRING
)

CREATE TABLE Buildings (
  building_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name STRING,
  architect_id UUID,
  construction_date DATE,
  location STRING
)

CREATE TABLE Blueprints (
  blueprint_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  building_id UUID,
  blueprint_data BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE Construction_Companies (
  company_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name STRING,
  location STRING
)

CREATE TABLE Contracts (
  contract_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  building_id UUID,
  company_id UUID,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)
